slogan: Eyad Omar, web developer that aspires to design and build attractive modern websites.
name: Eyad Omar AbdElAziz
about-me: I was born in Egypt in 2000.My father got me my first computer when I was nine years old, and I've been obsessed with computers ever since. At 2019, I enrolled at MTI's computer science faculty .I graduated in 2023 with a 3.6 GPA. Of course, I am grateful to my college for teaching the fundamentals of computer science, but what has truly defined me is my self-study in front end development since 2021. I've built dozens of websites using various tools and am eager to build more.
